  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_2",
    "text": "生态问题",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.1292422129242213,
      0.2259552042160738,
      0.22501162250116225,
      0.2463768115942029
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_3",
    "text": "1.水土流失问题",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12738261273826126,
      0.25757575757575757,
      0.28637842863784285,
      0.27733860342555994
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_4",
    "text": "我国典型地区：黄土高原、南方低山丘陵地区",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14504881450488144,
      0.2878787878787879,
      0.5764760576476058,
      0.3096179183135705
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_5",
    "text": "产生的原因：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1515574151557415,
      0.3188405797101449,
      0.2798698279869828,
      0.3386034255599473
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_6",
    "text": "(1) 自然原因：季风气候降水集中，多暴雨：地表植被稀少，黄十质疏松黄高原。 (2)人为原因：植被的破坏：不合理的耕作制度；开矿。 治理的措施：压缩农业用地，扩大林，草种植面积；植树造林；小流域综合治理。 治理的意义：有利于因地制宜地进行产业结构的调整，使农林牧副全面发展， 可以增加农民收入.促进当地经济发展，改善农民生活条件，提高生活质量：有利于改善 当地的生态环境，建立良性生态系统：建立生态农业模式，有利于促进生态和经济可持 续发展。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09390980939098094,
      0.35046113306982873,
      0.9177126917712691,
      0.5586297760210803
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_7",
    "text": "2.荒漠化问题",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.099488609948861,
      0.5994729907773386,
      0.2547652254765225,
      0.6212121212121212
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_8",
    "text": "我国典型的地区：西北地区(新疆、青海、内蒙等地) 产生的原因：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12645281264528127,
      0.6304347826086957,
      0.6536494653649465,
      0.6824769433465085
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_9",
    "text": "(1)自然原因：全球变暖、蒸发旺盛；处于内陆地区，降水少；鼠害；蝗害。 (2)人为原因：过度放牧：过度樵采：过度开垦：水阅源的不合理利用；交通线等 工程建设保护不当。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08833100883310088,
      0.6936758893280632,
      0.905625290562529,
      0.7786561264822134
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_10",
    "text": "治理措施.",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.1292422129242213,
      0.7872200263504612,
      0.2584844258484426,
      0.8076416337285902
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99_11",
    "text": "制定草场保护的法律、法规，加强管理：控制载畜量：营造三北防护林建 设；退耕还林、还牧；建设人工草场；推广轮牧：禁止采伐发莱等。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08926080892608089,
      0.8181818181818182,
      0.9195722919572292,
      0.8774703557312253
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_99",
    "order": 12
  }
]